<Vertical>
  <Markdown>
    ## DefaultGrader Demo

    DefaultGrader accepts any answer and returns a fixed score/feedback.
    Useful for open-ended questions or reflection prompts.
  </Markdown>

  <CapaProblem title="Open-Ended Reflection">
    <Markdown>What did you learn from this lesson? (Any answer accepted)</Markdown>

    <DefaultGrader score="1" feedback="Thank you for your reflection!">
      <LineInput/>
    </DefaultGrader>
  </CapaProblem>

  <Markdown>
    ### Feedback Without Full Credit

    You can give feedback with partial or zero credit:
  </Markdown>

  <CapaProblem title="Partial Credit Example">
    <Markdown>Write anything you'd like:</Markdown>

    <DefaultGrader score="0.5" feedback="Thanks for participating! Partial credit awarded.">
      <LineInput/>
    </DefaultGrader>
  </CapaProblem>
</Vertical>
